{"word":"κλώζω","slug":"κλώζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n58063\" key=\"klw/zw\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">κλώζω</orth>, of the sound made by jackdaws, as <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κρώζω</foreign> of crows, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0542.tlg001:5:89\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Poll.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.89</biblScope></bibl>. <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n58063.0\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">make a similar sound in token of disapprobation, hoot</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg021.perseus-grc1:226\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.226</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0640.tlg001:3:71\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Alciphr.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.71</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Phot.</author> </bibl>:—<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pass.\">Pass.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0284.tlg001.perseus-grc1:34(50).7\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Aristid.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Or.\">Or.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">34(50).7</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κλώσσω</foreign>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}